### What changed

- Expanded `description:` to mention GraphQL signature lag and gpg-agent pre-warming
- Added two new "When to Use" triggers:
  - `gh pr view --json commits` shows `signature.state=null` for newly-pushed commits
  - sub-agent push produces unsigned commits despite global `commit.gpgsign=true`
- Added new Verified Workflow subsection "GraphQL Lag â€” Use REST for Verification"
- Added new Verified Workflow subsection "Pre-Warm gpg-agent in Sub-Agent Shells"
- Added two Failed Attempts rows (trust GraphQL UNSIGNED as authoritative; re-upload GPG key)
